description:
We're planning a bit of a different event in December since everyone is going to be busy. More details will be announced soon - but we're hoping to have a relaxed social gathering.

Join us at the Kings St Brew house for a chilled out evening just chatting and socialising, and we can all plan together where the evening goes from there
title: December Social event - 6th Dec 🍺🍷🥳🎉
